ve a fairly high minimum wait time - possibly too long when doing I/O on low-latency channels, for example. That's why I ended up using [this mix of `yield` and `sleep`](https://github.com/oschulz/ParallelProcessingTools.jl/blob/72ce5614ea2ffd484ea819d7383485240b5d6fe6/src/waiting.jl#L21) in ParallelProcessingTools.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/comments/2290755582/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null}}

